                            <comment id="14053141" author="junrao" created="Sun, 6 Jul 2014 15:52:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I think it would be better if we document it as required and get rid of the default.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14053248" author="danielcompton" created="Sun, 6 Jul 2014 23:20:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Great, I&apos;ll prepare a patch, documenting it as mandatory and removing the default value.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
